{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>On the shore of the Forgotten Island, a lost puppet wakes up.</strong></h2>Cast away by The Hand, the entity that once guided her, she will have to make her way up to the top of the mountain in order to find a way back home.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945720/extras/Liverpool-IslandTest_Modular-WindowsMacLinux-Unity2022.3.21f1_DX11_2024-04-0616-06-10-ezgif.com-crop.gif?t=1729418614\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Freely discover a small open world island at your own pace!</strong></h2>The whole island is there for you to explore. You can walk, jump, find and unlock shortcuts, and discover hidden places all around it!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Make new friends and unveil a charming and emotional story!</strong></h2>Many characters inhabit the Forgotten Island, meet them all, learn their stories and do your best to give a helping hand. Who knows, maybe they can teach you a thing or two!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Help the characters of the island trough different mini-games!</strong></h2>Each character unlocks a unique mini-game, you'll have to find and beat them all!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Complete extra objectives to get hidden rewards!</strong></h2>There are special rewards waiting for you if you complete the extra objectives in the game!<br><br><strong>Coming soon for PC!</strong>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945720/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729418614","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945720/page.bg.jpg?t=1729418614","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945720/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729418614","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945720/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729418614","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"descript